---
title: Priority Scheduling + Iterative Deepening Proof Search
---
flowchart TD
    A[Input sequent] --> B[Preprocess / parse problem]
    B --> C[Set global deadline = now + timeout]
    C --> D[Set depth limit = 0]

    D --> T{Global timeout / cancel?}
    T -->|yes| H[Return Timeout / Cancelled]
    T -->|no| S[Run bounded backward search]

    S --> R[Find applicable rules]
    R --> P[Select first non-empty priority class]
    P --> Q[Try scheduled rules recursively]

    Q --> E{Closed proof found?}
    E -->|yes| F[Return Provable]

    E -->|no| G{Timeout / cancel?}
    G -->|yes| H

    G -->|no| I{Depth limit exhausted?}
    I -->|yes| J[Increase depth limit]
    J --> T

    I -->|no| K[Return Unknown / NotProvable if saturated]
